      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the hood and roof, and a few small dings on the passenger side doors. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and some staining consistent with regular use. Mechanically, it runs well, though it may soon require routine maintenance like new brake pads and a tire rotation. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done without any hidden surprises.",
