      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a mechanically sorted example of the legendary S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated straight-six features six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS, delivering linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Essential preventative maintenance is documented, including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The chassis has been stabilized with rear subframe reinforcement plates to mitigate fatigue, while the suspension maintains factory-spec geometry for precise turn-in. Power is managed via a 6-speed manual transmission and a mechanical limited-slip differential. This is a high-performance driver\u2019s car with all critical hardware addressed.",
