      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This 2018 BMW 540i xDrive is a beautifully maintained luxury sedan that perfectly balances performance and sophistication. The Mediterranean Blue Metallic paint shines brilliantly, showing only minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the smoke-free cabin features premium Oyster Dakota leather with fine-line wood accents; the seats remain firm and supportive, with only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic feature, from the heads-up display to the multi-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio. It recently underwent a full inspection, receiving new brake pads and a fresh synthetic oil service. The turbocharged inline-six engine delivers smooth, effortless power, and the tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy the ultimate driving machine.",
